    "ParentObjectID": "advanced_copper_tools_copper_cauldron",
    "LocalizationKey": "Advanced_Copper_Tools_CopperCauldron_CardDescription",
    "DefaultText": "A broad copper cauldron with a large open basin. Place it on a campfire or fireplace to heat it up and cook or brew several items at once. Holds 30% more liquid than a clay cauldron. Food stored inside spoils 30% slower than normal."
  },
