    "LocalizationKey": "Advanced_Copper_Tools_CopperCauldron_CardHelpSection",
    "DefaultText": "<b>Usage:</b> Fill at a river or lake, then place on a campfire or fireplace to heat up. Temperature must reach 100 before cooking or boiling begins. Holds up to 6240 ml of liquid. Copper slows food spoilage by 30% while stored inside."
